tafsir[28]{c,v,t}:
  26,84,"Waﾉ預naa mi jaﾅ逆a labaaﾉ熔 e mantoore moﾆｴﾆｴere e ﾉ容n gire aroyay ﾉ容 ﾉ殿awo am."
  26,85,"Waﾉ預a lam jeyaaﾉ熔 e ﾉ兎n ronooﾉ兎 galleeji Aljanna ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁 neemintoo e nder muuﾉ蓉m jeyaaﾉ兎 Maaﾉ預 gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, hoﾉ擁naa lam e nder majji."
  26,86,"Yawtanaa baaba am; kanko o laatinoke jeyaaﾉ熔 e majjuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n gaay Goonga kan sabu sirku ngun, Ibraahiima du'anii ben makko ko adii ﾉ殿nngannde mo wonndema kanko ko o jeyaaﾉ熔 e yimﾉ兎 Jahiimi ﾉ兎n. Tuma nde ﾉ蓉m ﾉ殿nngannoo mo, o danndii mo o du'anaaki mo [hannde kadi]."
  26,87,"Wata A wirtiroyam Lepte ﾉ容n ﾃ疎lnde yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n immintinoytee fii hasboore nden."
  26,88,"ﾃ疎lnde nde nafataa e muuﾉ蓉m jawdi ndi neﾉ遼熔 on faggitii ﾉ蓉m ka aduna makko, wanaa kadi ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 ﾉ兎 o laatinoo himo wallitora ﾉ蓉m."
  26,89,"Si wanaa on arduﾉ熔 ka Alla e ﾉ兎rnde hisunde; hara sirku e naafiqaaku alaa e mayre, yiingo e hawtaare alaa e mayre, haray pellet, kanko o nafturay jawdi makko ndi o nafkunoo ndin ka Laawol Alla, e ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 makko wonuﾉ兎 du'anaade mo ﾉ兎n kadi."
  26,90,"Aljanna on ﾉ殿nnanee hulirooﾉ兎 Joomi mu'un ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔ftagol Yamiraaﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n, e woﾉ遼擁tagol haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n."
  26,91,"Ka Mofturu Yiite ngen feﾃｱﾃｱinanee majjuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎n majjuﾉ兎 gaay Diina Goongaha kan."
  26,92,"ﾆ‘ wi'anee ka maﾆｴinngol ﾉ兎: Honto ko wonunoﾉ熔n rewude kon immorde e sanamuuji ﾉ擁n?"
  26,93,"On reway ﾉ擁 gaanin Alla? Taw si ﾉ擁 walliray on haﾉ預nngol on Lepte Alla ﾉ容n, kaa kannji ﾉ擁 wallay ko'e-majji?"
  26,94,"Woﾉ橡兎 e maﾉ橡兎 werlee e hoore woﾉ橡兎 ka Jahiima e ﾉ兎n majjinﾉ兎 ﾉ兎."
  26,95,"E wallooﾉ兎 Ibliisa ﾉ兎n immorde e Seytanuuji ﾉ擁n fow, hay gootil e majji ittintinaaka."
  26,96,"ﾆ‘n sirkooﾉ兎 wonunooﾉ兎 rewde tanaa Alla, ﾉ兎 jogitii ﾉ兎 kafidaaﾉ兎 gaanin Alla, tawi kanﾉ兎 hiﾉ兎 wennjondirde e ﾉ兎n rewnooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 gaanin Alla, ﾉ兎 wi'i:"
  26,97,"Men woondirii Alla gomﾉ擁i hari men laatike e nder majjere ﾉ殿nngunde gaayi Goonga kan."
  26,98,"Tuma nde men fotindirnoo on e Joom tageefooji ﾉ擁n fow majji, men rewiri on wano men rewirta Mo non."
  26,99,"Majjinaali men gaayi Laawol Goongawol ngol si wanaa ﾉ兎n bonﾉ兎 nodduﾉ兎 faade e rewugol ﾉ兎 gaanin Alla."
  26,100,"Laatanaaki men tefooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 no tefanoya men ka Alla fii yo O danndu men immorde e lepte Makko ﾉ容n."
  26,101,"Laatanaaki men giﾉ熔 laaﾉ砥ﾉ熔 giggol mo no hiwa men o tefanoya men."
  26,102,"Sinndo no woodannoo men artireede ka ngurndam aduna, men wona jeyaaﾉ兎 e gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎n."
  26,103,"Pellet, wonii e koo ko jaﾅ逆aa ﾉ熔o immorde e fillayee fii Ibraahiima (yo o his), e waﾉ葉inirde fennuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n tasakuyee, wonannde taskotooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 heewude e maﾉ橡兎 wonaali gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎."
  26,104,"Anndu Joomi maaﾉ預 -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ko Kanko woni tedduﾉ熔 Yoﾉ鍍otooﾉ熔 ayﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, Yurmeteeﾉ熔 on tuubuﾉ熔 e maﾉ橡兎."
  26,105,"Yimﾉ兎 Nuuhu ﾉ兎n fenni Nulaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, tuma nde ﾉ兎 fennunoo Nuuhu (yo o his)."
  26,106,"Tuma nde Saalihu musiﾉ遼熔 maﾉ橡兎 on ka dammbe (asko) wi'annoo ﾉ兎: Enee, on hulataa Alla, acciron rewugol tanaa Makko sabu kulol Makko?!"
  26,107,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaaﾉ熔 mooﾉ熔n, Alla Nulii lam e mooﾉ熔n, ko mi hoolaaﾉ熔 mi ﾉ兎ydataa e dow ko Alla Wahayini kon e am, mi uytataa kadi."
  26,108,"Huliree Alla ﾉ熔ftagol Yamiraaﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n e woﾉ遼擁tagol haﾉ預ani Makko ﾉ擁n, ﾉ熔ftee lam e ko mi yamirta on kon, e ko mi haﾉ預ta on kon e muuﾉ蓉m."
  26,109,"Mi ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬raali on njoﾉ電i fii ko mi yottinanta Joomi am kon e mooﾉ熔n, njoﾉ電i am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Alla Jooma tageefooji ﾉ擁n wanaa e tanaa Makko."
  26,110,"Huliree Alla ﾉ熔ftagol Yamiraaﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n e woﾉ遼擁tagol haﾉ預ani Makko ﾉ擁n, ﾉ熔ftee lam e ko mi yamirta on kon, e ko mi haﾉ預ta on kon e muuﾉ蓉m."
  26,111,"Yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n wi'ani mo: Enee, hara men gomﾉ擁nte -an Nuuhu- men jokka ko adduﾉ預a kon men gollira, hara le pellet, jokkuﾉ兎 ma ﾉ兎n ko e yimﾉ兎 jaasuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 jeyaako e hoohooﾉ兎 e teddinaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n alaa e maﾉ橡兎?!"
